<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "coding_pfp.png", width: 300, alt: "coding_pfp.png", class: 'coding_pfp.png' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I'm a 17 year old student at Jordan High School with aspirations to become a computer programmer. I applied and was accepted into the CTS (Code To Success) program at Jordan High and through a 9 week course which I graduated from, built this website via tutorials made by Jordan Hudgens.</p>

        <p></p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              TazWorks LLC
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Sizzling Platter LLC
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Willow Canyon Elementary
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Eastmont Middle School
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jordan High School
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>